  "name": "Xero / MYOB Trial Accounts for Testing",
  "body": "<h1 data-id=\"xero-myob-trial-accounts-for-testing\">Xero / MYOB Trial Accounts for Testing</h1>\n<h2 data-id=\"xero\"><strong>Xero</strong></h2>\n<p>Xero will allow a full functioning account as a free 30 day trial which can be used with the automatic Xero Integration.</p>\n<p>Go to <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://galaxy.maropost.com/home/leaving?allowTrusted=1&amp;target=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.xero.com%2Fau%2F\">https://www.xero.com/au/</a> </p>\n<ul><li>Click Try Xero for free on the top right</li><li>Create an Account by entering your details</li><li>Setup a password via the confirmation email</li></ul><p><img alt=\"rtaImage - 2023-07-10T061745.985.jpeg\" src=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000pplFsEAI.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000pplFsEAI.jpg 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000pplFsEAI.jpg 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000pplFsEAI.jpg 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000pplFsEAI.jpg 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000pplFsEAI.jpg 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000pplFsEAI.jpg 2000w, https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000pplFsEAI.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></p>\n<ul><li>Enter a <strong>Business Name</strong></li><li>Select an <strong>Industry</strong></li><li>Under <strong>Do you have employees?</strong> select <strong>No</strong></li><li>Click <strong>Start Trial</strong></li></ul><p> </p>\n<h2 data-id=\"myob\"><strong>MYOB</strong></h2>\n<p>MYOB will only allow you to create Local Files as a free 30 day trial, which cannot be used with the automatic MYOB Integration.<br/><br/>It can, however, be used for testing via the Accounting Data Export.</p>\n<p>Go to <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://galaxy.maropost.com/home/leaving?allowTrusted=1&amp;target=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.myob.com%2Fau%2Faccounting-software%2Faccountright\">https://www.myob.com/au/accounting-software/accountright</a> </p>\n<ul><li>Scroll down to the Pricing area</li><li>Under AccountRight Plus click Try Free for 30 Days</li><li>Create an Account by entering your details</li><li>Click Download AccountRight if the software is not already installed</li><li>Setup a password via the confirmation email</li></ul><p><img alt=\"rtaImage - 2023-07-10T061757.170.jpeg\" src=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppl8ZEAQ.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppl8ZEAQ.jpg 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppl8ZEAQ.jpg 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppl8ZEAQ.jpg 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppl8ZEAQ.jpg 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppl8ZEAQ.jpg 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppl8ZEAQ.jpg 2000w, https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppl8ZEAQ.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>",
